freq:
	no idea how it's stored yet. Close values seem close.
	Seems the same as shift freq if both are set to the same value - this indicates the leading 01 is likely not part of it
	86489A00 = 10.11111
	Helpful because we are allowed to program in a zero offset frequency, which is zero.
	
	00000000 = 0.00000
	0A000000 = 0.00001		0x0A = 10
	14000000 = 0.00002		0x14 = 20
	1E000000 = 0.00003		0x1E = 30
	
	0.00001Mhz = 10Hz
	
	Little endian format
	
	F0490200 = 150000 - 0.150Mhz
	

step:
	there are 18 settings, can't set all for any frequency range
	so far observed
	0x07 = 25k
	0x09 = 50k
	0x0c = 150k

tsq mode:
	0x00 = off
	0x03 = TSQ
	0x04 = SQ
	0x05 = DCS

DCS:
	0x00 = 023
	0x01 = 025
	0x67 = 754
	
modulation:
	0x00 = FM
	0x01 = AM
	0x02 = WFM
	0x03 = LSB
	0x04 = USB
	0x05 = CW

shift:
	0x00 = none
	0x01 = +
	0x02 = -

skip: 
	0x00 = no
	0x01 = yes
